description: Don’t miss your chance to make South Boston your new home.  The main floor of this single family home consists of a large kitchen with a double-wall oven and plenty of cabinet space.  The open floor plan leads into a dining room and a half-bathroom just down the hall, perfect for entertaining!  Down stairs includes a living area and a small kitchenette with a full bathroom, exterior access and a rear balcony. The spacious bedrooms are located on the second floor with additional living area on the top floor. New furnace in 2019 and a fenced-in backyard are just some of the bonus features of this listing.  Come and take a look at our open houses. This one will not last!
